A MAN has vanished after he failed to return home from work.David O'Donnell was working in Cumnock, Ayrshire yesterday afternoon but did not return to his home.No contact has been made with the 35-year-old since 12.10pm yesterday afternoon.His sister, Lynsey O' Donnell, has made an urgent plea for information on her brother's whereabouts and said his two young sons are &quot;missing their daddy&quot;.A Police Scotland spokeswoman said: &quot;I can confirm there is a man named David O'Donnell from the area.&quot;Police are working to gather information.&quot;Anyone with information is asked to contact Police Scotland on 101.